725
01:07:36,750 --> 01:07:38,950
Je to super!

726
01:07:39,190 --> 01:07:40,530
Pozerali ste včera futbal?

727
01:07:40,530 --> 01:07:41,330
Ja hej.

728
01:07:41,390 --> 01:07:42,730
Messi dal skvelý gól!

729
01:07:42,790 --> 01:07:43,130
Hej!

730
01:07:43,230 --> 01:07:45,530
A však je Neymar úplne cool?

731
01:07:45,630 --> 01:07:48,830
Toto je pre vás od toho pána.

732
01:07:48,890 --> 01:07:49,970
Čo?

733
01:07:54,060 --> 01:07:55,430
Ďakujeme.

734
01:07:55,460 --> 01:07:56,580
Ďakujeme.

735
