739
01:08:03,570 --> 01:08:05,530
To určite nie!

740
01:08:05,560 --> 01:08:06,130
Čo ty, Saki?

741
01:08:06,130 --> 01:08:08,960
Nie, vďaka.
Z toho biznisu som už dávno von.

742
01:08:08,990 --> 01:08:09,430
Aha.

743
01:08:10,230 --> 01:08:10,960
Nazdravie!

744
01:08:10,960 --> 01:08:11,850
Ozaj!

745
01:08:11,930 --> 01:08:13,430
Poďte sem, rýchlo!

746
01:08:13,490 --> 01:08:14,110
Čo je?

747
01:08:14,370 --> 01:08:14,880
Tam!

748
01:08:15,390 --> 01:08:16,960
Čo, Tokyo Tower?

749
01:08:17,300 --> 01:08:19,160
Má vianočné svetlá!

750
01:08:19,160 --> 01:08:20,230
Vážne!

751
01:08:20,260 --> 01:08:21,640
Na tom som tiež pracovala.

752
01:08:23,290 --> 01:08:24,970
Je to krásne!

753
01:08:25,230 --> 01:08:27,010
Na Štedrý večer bude dúhová.

754
01:08:27,280 --> 01:08:30,530
