780
01:09:26,630 --> 01:09:27,130
Hej.

781
01:09:27,230 --> 01:09:27,630
Wow!

782
01:09:27,660 --> 01:09:28,840
Super, že?

783
01:09:29,930 --> 01:09:33,230
